title: Cammy Gaiden
original_name: スーパーストリートファイター 2 キャミィ外伝
sinopse:
Cammy, an amnesiac MI6 agent, fights the forces of Shadowlaw, whilst trying to regain her shattered memories.

Note: Nakahira released an extra chapter for Cammy Gaiden in the SF2 Movie film book "Gekijouyou Animation Street Fighter II".
